longBusinessSummary: Immunovia AB (publ), a diagnostic company, engages in developing and commercializing blood tests for the early detection of cancer and autoimmune diseases based on its proprietary test platform IMMray in Sweden and internationally. Its pipeline comprises early-phase research projects in collaboration with academic centers; and diagnostic tests in pancreatic cancer and rheumatoid arthritis diagnostics. Immunovia AB (publ) was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
